{
  "stem": "888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or what do you call it, you know, where military people live?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Camps, I suppose, you know, military camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And neither one, you know, were afraid to-- with Jews, to start up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, you know, when the Hungarians came in and there was a lot of Romanian population, the Romanian population there-- their priests wear also beards, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then for a while, when they came in they started-- you know, of course, a Jew, you know, would pull their beard or cut their beard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, it was almost an everyday event.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But also-- Did you ever see any of it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not necessarily.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I've been chased many times by soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, many times we were chased by--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think I was a little faster than they were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was an occasion, you know, that you had to really run for-- you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's-- and of course, and as it, as it was going on year by year, you know, Hungarians, you know, of course, you know, got involved in the war with Russia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then anti-Semitism, you know, grew, you know, tremendously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, you know, then for a while, in the '40s, when the Hungarians came in, they took yet some Jews, you know, to the military, you know, and sent them to the front, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but then later on, you know, they changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't take them to military service, only to work details.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, they were sending out different-- you know, to different places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the front, you know, and different-- to Poland, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
